[SIZE=3]Installation[/SIZE]

1. Download the latest release from [URL="https://github.com/Mctalian/RPGLootFeed/releases/latest"]GitHub[/URL] or right here on WoW Interface.
2. Extract the downloaded file into your World of Warcraft Interface/AddOns directory.
3. Restart World of Warcraft and enable RPGLootFeed in the AddOns menu.

